{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":154,"Text":"你們有甚麼理由？你們怎麼這樣判斷呢？"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":155,"Text":"你們還不覺悟嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":156,"Text":"難道你們有一個明証嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":157,"Text":"拿出你們的經典來吧，倘若你們是誠實的人！"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":158,"Text":"他們妄言他與精靈之間，有姻親關係。精靈確已知道他們將被拘禁"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":159,"Text":"——超絕哉真主！他是超乎他們的敘述的"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":160,"Text":"——惟真主的純潔的眾僕，不被拘禁。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":161,"Text":"你們和你們所崇拜的，"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":162,"Text":"絕不能把任何人引誘去崇拜他們，"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":163,"Text":"除非是將入火獄的人。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":164,"Text":"（眾天神說）：「我們人人都有一個指定的地位，"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":165,"Text":"我們必定是排班的，"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":166,"Text":"我們必定是讚頌真主的。」"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":167,"Text":"他們的確常說："},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":168,"Text":"「假若我們有古人所遺留的教誨，"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":169,"Text":"那末，我們必是真主的純潔的僕人。」"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":170,"Text":"他們卻不信真主，他們不久就知道了。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":171,"Text":"我對我所派遣的僕人們已有約言在先了，"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":172,"Text":"他們必定是被援助的，"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":173,"Text":"我的軍隊，必定是勝利的。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":174,"Text":"你暫時退避他們吧！"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":175,"Text":"你看著吧！他們不久就看見了。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":176,"Text":"難道他們要求我的刑罰早日實現嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":177,"Text":"我的刑罰一旦降於他們的庭院的時候，被警告者的早晨，真惡劣呀！"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":178,"Text":"你暫時退避他們吧！"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":179,"Text":"你看著吧！他們不久就看見了。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":180,"Text":"超絕哉你的主——尊榮的主宰！他是超乎他們的敘述的。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":181,"Text":"祝眾使者平安！"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":182,"Text":"一切讚頌，全歸真主——全世界的主！"}]}